name: xamoom-android-sdk
body:
### Welcome to xamoom-android-sdk
xamoom-android-sdk is a framework for the xamoom-cloud api. So you can write your own applications for the xamoom-cloud.

### First Steps
Please look at our wiki: https://github.com/xamoom/xamoom-android-sdk/wiki

### Support or Contact
Check out the documentation at http://xamoom.github.io/xamoom-android-sdk/docs/html/index.html or contact apps@xamoom.com.
